@startuml
actor UserA
actor UserB
participant "Client A" as CA
participant "Client B" as CB
participant "STOMP /app/chat/{id}" as STOMP
participant MessageController
participant MessageService
database DB
participant "Broker /topic/conversation/{id}" as Broker
UserA -> CA: type message + send
CA -> STOMP: SEND /app/chat/{conversationId}
STOMP -> MessageController: inbound payload
MessageController -> MessageService: persist(conversationId, content)
MessageService -> DB: INSERT message
DB --> MessageService: saved message
MessageService --> MessageController: MessageResponse
MessageController -> Broker: broadcast response
Broker --> CA: MESSAGE frame
Broker --> CB: MESSAGE frame
CA --> UserA: UI append without reload
CB --> UserB: UI append without reload
@enduml
